overview.en: UAB (US Artbank) created by US Artbank International Limited (USABI), is an investment holding company at the apex of traditional and digital art industry. USABI has a vision to represent and share the treasures of unique artists that continue to extend the limits and create new boundaries in the art world. We are the exclusive owners and invested in the renowned Gold Art of Kim Il Tae. USABI have established presence in Malaysia, Indonesia, Taiwan, China, Middle East and Russia. USABI is to issued Gold Art backed Initial Coin Offering (ICO) for artist, owners of art and new investors in art objects. Retail investorsï¼Œmuseums, galleries, global funds and art-lovers will be the participants and market players in this eco-system.
